  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, org.springframework.validation.BindingResult, org.springframework.validation.Errors

    public class WebExchangeBindException
extends ServerWebInputException
implements org.springframework.validation.BindingResult
    A specialization of ServerWebInputException thrown when after data binding and validation failure. Implements BindingResult (and its super-interface Errors) to allow for direct analysis of binding and validation errors.
    从以下版本开始:
    5.0
